title: Madonna - Miles Away (Official recalled promo video - DVD RIP)
description:
The long awaited promotional video for the third single from Madonna's 2008 album 'Hard Candy' was unintentionally released on a promotional VJ DVD and released to clubs throughout Europe. Warner has already recalled these DVDs, which will make this item very hard to come by!

This is a DVD rip from said promotional DVD as originally hosted by http://www.absolumentmadonna.fr/ 

This is a .VOB file, so make sure you have the proper codecs installed to play it back!
